2天 <br />\nemail..sms 打電話都找不到女友了...晚上我在她公司樓下等她..等了半小時，有警察過來查問我，說有人報警受到跟蹤及騷擾.... 我知是她報警的..當時我眼淚不停流出來了..... <br />\n<br />\n痾唔出屎的第13天 <br />\n老細email同我講..公司生意不太好要栽員...願即時補兩個月人工 不過要我即刻走.....當天下班看見招職公司登請人的廣告...我看了眼淚不停流出來了.. <br />\n<br />\n痾唔出屎的第14天 <br />\n身體發出強烈屎臭...面上長滿暗瘡..膚色己呈啡黃色..從FB看見女友info寫住..和XXX穩定交往.還用iphone4和那xxx自拍...她原來和另一個男仔一齊了...我眼淚不停流出來了... <br />\n<br />\n痾吾出屎的第15天 <br />\n痾得出屎了! 痾得出屎了!!!!!還痾了很多...我開心得流下眼淚!!不停流出來....可惜一齊都太遲了...."},{"pid":"1e8a25ef10909148261a1ca903220ebf7db80a10","tid":712585,"uid":106506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T07:59:49.000Z","msg":"人地話靚女唔屙屎<br />\n佢又咩事唔屙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"442cce203f8dd04e4aa88edb1133f20b3f591335","tid":712585,"uid":106506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e8a25ef10909148261a1ca903220ebf7db80a10","tid":712585,"uid":106506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T07:59:49.000Z","msg":"人地話靚女唔屙屎<br />\n佢又咩事唔屙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T08:00:18.000Z","msg":"屙唔出"},{"pid":"ed3cd5da8d3afcbf8c5c36188a100456a376284f","tid":712585,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T08:03:39.000Z","msg":"徒手挖掘"},{"pid":"61bd7534b7d21e2ed0a6f18fb795786421c6165d","tid":712585,"uid":61954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T08:07:15.000Z","msg":"挖礦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"099aeffcecc22e948f25fe3a3f5a705f394f5c3f","tid":712585,"uid":8048,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T08:08:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://wiki.komica.org/images/thumb/b/b2/Img1858.jpg/450px-Img1858.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwiki.komica.org%2Fimages%2Fthumb%2Fb%2Fb2%2FImg1858.jpg%2F450px-Img1858.jpg&h=54937356&s={S